-helical Dirac cone states,\ntherefore ruling out single-layer PtP$_2$ as a topological insulator. We expect\nthe example demonstrated in this work will stimulate interest in\ncomputationally identifying novel 2D materials from a variety of bulk materials\nwith the pyrite structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Aug 2018 00:51:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
